description:
The well gives the Magistrate back her power and she transforms into Shiroageha, but her memories are lost.  She attacks Jinbei, and the power of the well makes Sanada much stronger.  Jinbei, who swore to fight until he dies, is faced with his last enemy.  The final battle begins!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: 月島仁兵衞 ここにあり!!!
